            "title": "歐股靠穩  汽車股向好",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">歐洲股市上升。工業股和汽車股表現較好。泛歐指數Stoxx 600收市反彈0.45%，報578點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"歐股 (AP圖片)\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250318_FI_source-ap_Britain_Financial_Markets-3.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"歐股 (AP圖片)\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250318_FI_source-ap_Britain_Financial_Markets-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">歐股 (AP圖片)</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">英國富時100指數收報9710點，升18點，升幅0.19%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">法國CAC指數收報8122點，升34點，升幅0.43%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">德國DAX指數收報23882點，升188點，升幅0.79%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">意大利富時MIB指數收報43519點，走高0.32%或138點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">西班牙IBEX 35指數收報16746點，上漲0.97%或160點。</p>\n</div>",
